 for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
    int leftSum = 0;
    int rightSum = 0;

    for (int j = 0; j < i; j++) {
        leftSum += nums[j];
    }

    for (int j = i + 1; j < n; j++) {
        rightSum += nums[j];
    }

    if (leftSum == rightSum) return i;
}  



[ left side ]  i  [ right side ]
0 ......... i-1   i+1 ....... n-1
So:
left loop → j = 0 → i-1
right loop → j = i+1 → n-1
